 KISS 的吉恩·西蒙斯在《与星共舞》中被指控厌女症后表示“我坚持我所说的每一句话” https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-gene-simmons-i-stand-by-every-word-accusations-misogyny-dancing-with-the-stars-3802021?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=吻-吉恩-西蒙斯-我支持每一个字的指责-厌女症-与星星共舞Max PilleyFri, 11 Oct 2024 18:24:20 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3802021 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gene_simmons_kiss.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gene_simmons_kiss.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gene_simmons_kiss-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gene_simmons_kiss-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gene_simmons_kiss-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gene_simmons_kiss-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gene_simmons_kiss-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位资深摇滚明星因在节目中担任客座评委时对女性参赛者的评论而被形容为“恶心”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-gene-simmons-i-stand-by-every-word-accusations-misogyny-dancing-with-the-stars-3802021">在《与星共舞》的厌女症指控</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上后，KISS 的吉恩·西蒙斯 (Gene Simmons) 表示，“我坚持我所说的每一句话”。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gene_simmons_kiss.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gene_simmons_kiss.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gene_simmons_kiss-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gene_simmons_kiss-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gene_simmons_kiss-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gene_simmons_kiss-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gene_simmons_kiss-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gene-simmons">吉恩·西蒙斯</a>表示，在收到厌女症指控后，他坚持自己对<i>《与星共舞》</i>的评论。</p><p>这位经验丰富的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kiss">KISS</a>歌手兼贝斯手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-gene-simmons-slammed-for-comments-dancing-with-the-stars-3801534">在本周（10 月 8 日）美国舞蹈节目的一集中引发了强烈反对</a>，他与 Bruno Tonioli、Derek Hough 和 Carrie Ann Inaba 一起担任该节目的客座评委。</p><p>一些观众批评他的一些评论，称他“恶心”、“不舒服”和“不尊重”，并称他更关注女选手的外表而不是她们的舞蹈能力。</p><p>例如，在回顾演员雷金纳德·维尔约翰逊的表演时，他说：“嘿，雷吉，你身边有一个美丽的女人，她可以扭转它、转动它，并且知道如何移动它等等。” ” </p><figure id="attachment_3785076" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3785076" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3785076" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/gene-simmons@2000x1270.jpg" alt="“Kiss”乐队主唱吉恩·西蒙斯站在瓦肯露天音乐会的舞台上" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/gene-simmons@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/gene-simmons@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/gene-simmons@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/gene-simmons@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/gene-simmons@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/gene-simmons@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3785076" class="wp-caption-text">吉恩·西蒙斯。图片来源：Axel Heimken/图片联盟来自 Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>现在，西蒙斯在节目中加倍努力，他告诉《 <a href="https://www.dailymail.co.uk/video/tvshowbiz/video-3288171/Video-Gene-Simmons-stands-comments-Dancing-Stars.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>每日邮报》</i></a> ：“所有媒体都是标题党。我坚持我所说的每一句话。我玩得很开心。参赛者都很棒。演出很棒。观看演出。这很有趣。但媒体呢？每个人都有话要说。观看演出。这很有趣。每个人都度过了愉快的时光。”</p><p>这一集被称为“Hair Metal Night”，情侣们随着<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/whitesnake">Whitesnake</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bon-jovi">Bon Jovi</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aerosmith">Aerosmith</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/europe">Europe</a>等歌曲以及 KISS 的“Rock And Roll All Nite”跳舞。</p><p>在吉恩·西蒙斯 (Gene Simmons) 的其他新闻中，这位 KISS 贝斯手最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gene-simmons-claims-hes-reclaimed-the-word-asshole-3798060">表示，他对被称为“混蛋”很满意</a>，甚至暗示他“重新夺回”了这个词，并试图将其与“黑人占领了‘n’词”进行比较。</p><p>他最近还表示，对 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-fans-react-to-ticketmasters-dynamic-pricing-3789361">动态定价的使用</a>不满意的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲</a>粉丝<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-gene-simmons-says-oasis-fans-are-entitled-to-fuck-off-you-dont-like-the-ticket-pricing-dont-buy-a-ticket-3794072">“有权滚蛋”</a> ，并继续权衡<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smiths">史密斯乐队</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-gene-simmons-on-the-smiths-reunion-if-you-go-down-the-street-and-ask-the-general-person-whos-johnny-marr-they-wont-know-who-youre-talking-about-3793934">重聚的前景</a>。</p><p>然而，他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/linkin-park">林肯公园</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-gene-simmons-weighs-in-on-linkin-parks-new-singer-scientology-controversy-3794189">新歌手艾米丽·阿姆斯特朗</a>更为积极。 “新来的女歌手，太棒了。她很适合这个乐队。她听起来很棒，祝他们好运。生命是短暂的。走出去，尽情享受，享受它，”他说。</p><p> “林肯公园有粉丝，他们想听歌曲和音乐。为什么不呢？有一些乐队进行巡演，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lynyrd-skynyrd">比如 Lynyrd Skynyrd</a> ，还有很多乐队几乎没有任何原始成员或没有原始成员。人们想听这些歌曲。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-gene-simmons-i-stand-by-every-word-accusations-misogyny-dancing-with-the-stars-3802021">在《与星共舞》的厌女症指控</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上后，KISS 的吉恩·西蒙斯 (Gene Simmons) 表示，“我坚持我所说的每一句话”。</p> ;
